title: Murphy homers again, Mets sweep Cubs to reach World Series
text:
> Sports Murphy homers again, Mets sweep Cubs to reach World Series New York Mets' Daniel Murphy hits a two-run home run during the eighth inning of Game 4 of the National League baseball championship series against the Chicago Cubs Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015, in Chicago. (AP Photo/David Goldman)
